Joh 17:14</p>"},{"id":"tsk-gen-31-38","title":"Genesis 31:38","author":"R. A. Torrey (editor)","reference":{"book":"GEN","chapterStart":31,"verseStart":38,"chapterEnd":31,"verseEnd":38},"content":"<p>envied. 26:14-16; Ps 106:16; Ec 4:4; Isa 11:13; 26:11; Mt 27:18; Mr 15:10 Ac 7:9; 13:45; Ga 5:21; Tit 3:3; Jas 3:14-16; 4:5 observed. 24:31; Da 7:28; Lu 2:19,51</p>"},{"id":"tsk-gen-31-43","title":"Genesis 31:43","author":"R. A. Torrey (editor)","reference":{"book":"GEN","chapterStart":31,"verseStart":43,"chapterEnd":31,"verseEnd":43},"content":"<p>Dothan. 2Ki 6:13</p>"},{"id":"tsk-gen-31-48","title":"Genesis 31:48","author":"R. A. Torrey (editor)","reference":{"book":"GEN","chapterStart":31,"verseStart":48,"chapterEnd":31,"verseEnd":48},"content":"<p>stript. 3,31-33; 42:21; Ps 22:18; Mt 27:28 colours. or, pieces. 3</p>"},{"id":"tsk-gen-31-53","title":"Genesis 31:53","author":"R. A. Torrey (editor)","reference":{"book":"GEN","chapterStart":31,"verseStart":53,"chapterEnd":31,"verseEnd":53},"content":"<p>he rent. 34; 34:13; Nu 14:6; Jud 11:35; 2Ki 19:1; Job 1:20; Joe 2:13 Ac 14:14</p>"}]}